comments: Jordan (DEN) is firming up over his left foot and does not deliver illegal contact as the screen is set on Green (DAL).
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) moves forward into Dinwiddie's (DAL) space and initiates contact with Dinwiddie's front that affects his SQBR as he starts his dribble.
Powell (DAL) commits a take foul on Hyland (DEN).
Brown (DEN) brushes Doncic's (DAL) right side and marginal contact occurs as they move over the pick.
Brown (DEN) brings his left hand forward and marginal contact occurs with Doncic's (DAL) right hand/wrist after he releases the pass.
Hyland (DEN) and Powell (DAL) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Doncic (DAL) legally contests Porter Jr.'s (DEN) three point jump shot attempt. Both of Porter's feet are established behind the 3pt line during his shot attempt.
Green (DAL) establishes himself in Brown's (DEN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Brown (DEN) maintains a rested hand on Doncic's (DAL) side and marginal contact occurs as Doncic picks up his dribble near the elbow.
Doncic (DAL) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes three steps before coming to a stop near the elbow.
Jordan (DEN) and Powell (DAL) engage and disengage with one another prior to and after the shot attempt is released.
Powell (DAL) is moving forward as he follows the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Hyland's (DEN) front as Hyland secures the ball.
Green (DAL) is moving forward when marginal body and arm contact occurs with Hyland (DEN) after Hyland gains control of the loose ball.
Hyland (DEN) turns to pivot and marginal contact occurs with Green's (DAL) right arm, which is brought forward toward Hyland. Green's reaction is not consistent with the amount of contact.
Finney-Smith (DAL) and Brown (DEN) engage and disengage with one another as the pick is set.
Jordan (DEN) raises his arms in pursuit of the rebound and incidental contact occurs with Doncic's (DAL) left arm prior to Doncic gaining control of the ball.
DAL signals for and is awarded a timeout prior to the start of Doncic's (DAL) dribble.  Upon exiting the timeout, DAL should have been allowed to immediately advance the ball.
Brown (DEN) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Brown (DEN) and Nnaji (DEN) each legally contest Doncic's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
